OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FITV Granada Reports journalist Anna
OL,8,FYoussef reports on the firefighting
OL,9,Foperation to extinguish moorland fires
OL,10,Fat Tintwistle Moor.
OL,12,FFamilies say they been left without
OL,13,Fclear public health advice as
OL,14,Fcampaigners claim "apocalyptic"
OL,15,Fwildfire smoke pushes pollution to 13
OL,16,Ftimes the daily limit.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
