FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FResidents have been able to smell and
OL,8,Fsee the smoke from the wildfires
OL,9,Facross large parts of the North West
OL,10,Fas two fires continue to burn on
OL,11,Fmoorland in Greater Manchester and
OL,12,FDerbyshire.
OL,14,FCampaigners claim to have recorded a
OL,15,Fmeasurement that is around 13 times
OL,16,Fhigher than the recommended daily
OL,17,FWorld Health Organisation's (WHO)
OL,18,Fguideline limit by using a handheld
OL,19,FAtmoPro air quality monitor. This was
OL,20,Fan instantaneous measurement, however,
OL,21,Frather than a 24-hour average.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FRichard Bailey, coordinator of the
OL,8,FPeak District Moorland group, has
OL,9,Fdescribed the Tintwistle Moor
OL,10,Fwildfires as "really dangerous" as
OL,11,Fcommunities continue to help
OL,12,Fextinguish them.
OL,14,FHe said: "Given these winds and this
OL,15,Fheat, and the amount of vegetation
OL,16,Fthat is burning, it's apocalyptic.
OL,18,F"It's really dangerous. We were out on
OL,19,Fthe Saddleworth in 2018, and this is
OL,20,Fon that scale.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,F"We are absolutely doing our best to
OL,8,Ffight this fire and contain it, and
OL,9,Fstop it encroaching."
OL,11,FCommunities close to the fires on the
OL,12,Fhills are rallying around to support
OL,13,Fthe emergency crews trying to put them
OL,14,Fout.
OL,16,FMicklehurst Cricket Club, in Mossley,
OL,17,Fis collecting donations and cooking
OL,18,Ffor emergency crews and gamekeepers.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FMatt Barton, from the club's
OL,8,Fcommittee, said: "We've set up a
OL,9,Fdonation centre, we're accepting
OL,10,Fdonations, cooking meals, getting
OL,11,Fthings up to the base camp where the
OL,12,Ffire crews are in the Peak District.
OL,14,F"We're just doing what we can. Any
OL,15,Ffruit, energy drinks, water, obviously
OL,16,Fconditions aren't great. It's really
OL,17,Fwarm, so we're getting things up there
OL,18,Fas quickly as we can.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FHe added: "We're cooking three times a
OL,8,Fday: breakfast, dinner and tea. These
OL,9,Fguys are up there all night.
OL,11,F"They're on rotas, coming down, having
OL,12,Fa break and then going again. We're
OL,13,Fkeeping on top of things and keeping
OL,14,Fthem fed and watered.
OL,16,F"We didn't expect this amount of
OL,17,Fdonations that we've had so far. In
OL,18,Fterms of the response from the local
OL,19,Fand wider community, it has been
OL,20,Famazing."
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FParents have also expressed concern
OL,8,Fthat there are no dedicated school air
OL,9,Fpollution alerts to reduce children's
OL,10,Fexposure.
OL,12,FSome local schools made the decision
OL,13,Ftoday to shut early.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,FLiz Godfrey, Greater Manchester
OL,8,Fcoordinator for Mums for Lungs said:
OL,9,F"Families can see the smoke, they can
OL,10,Fsmell it and they can taste it.
OL,11,FParents are understandably worried
OL,12,Fabout their children breathing this
OL,13,Fair, yet there has been no obvious
OL,14,Fpublic health warning telling people
OL,15,Fhow to protect themselves from the
OL,16,Fhealth effects of wildfire smoke.
OL,18,F"Why are Greater Manchester residents
OL,19,Fnot being warned?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,368,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1784220475
OL,3,CCampaigners call for public health
OL,4,Cmessaging as 'apocalyptic' wildfires
OL,5,Cburn
OL,7,F"Residents need clear health advice,
OL,8,Fschools need guidance, and vulnerable
OL,9,Fpeople deserve timely warnings when
OL,10,Fair pollution reaches hazardous
OL,11,Flevels."
OL,13,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,14,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,15,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,16,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
